实，不要那么不耐烦/你的粉丝很高兴认为这是我的到期/甚至你使用的照片、笑话和药物/迈巴赫手套和他用来减少通货膨胀的药物/操纵大师，你竞标炒作。”</em></p><p>据<a href="https://x.com/XXL/status/1788230184170082548" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>XXL</em></a>报道，这段视频获得了超过 100 万次点赞——这是他与拉马尔不和中所有歌曲中点赞最多的。在<em><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/C6uDXl7xc8O/?hl=en">《嘻哈狼》</a></em>的博文下面，一些粉丝认为这是由于“德雷克仇恨列车”造成的。</p><p>一位用户写道：“仇恨列车太疯狂了。他需要消失一分钟。音乐会变得如此垃圾，以至于人们会开始想要他的音乐。肯德里克不够稳定。所以现在就享受吧。我记得<a href="/artists/jay-z">Jay-Z</a>实际上也经历过同样的事情，因为人们开始攻击他。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C6uDXl7xc8O/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.